description: Manage and configure Azure Firewall NAT rules.

commands.name: az network firewall nat-rule collection delete
commands.summary: Delete an Azure Firewall NAT rule collection.
commands.syntax:
az network firewall nat-rule collection delete [--collection-name]
                                               [--firewall-name]
                                               [--ids]
                                               [--resource-group]
                                               [--subscription]

commands.name: az network firewall nat-rule collection list
commands.summary: List Azure Firewall NAT rule collections.
commands.syntax:
az network firewall nat-rule collection list --firewall-name
                                             --resource-group

commands.name: az network firewall nat-rule collection show
commands.summary: Get the details of an Azure Firewall NAT rule collection.
commands.syntax:
az network firewall nat-rule collection show [--collection-name]
                                             [--firewall-name]
                                             [--ids]
                                             [--resource-group]
                                             [--subscription]
